summary: This document is an invoice from FedEx to NYSG LLC for shipping services rendered. It details the charges incurred for a shipment picked up on August 1, 2003, and includes information about the billing and shipping addresses, as well as contact information for FedEx Revenue Services.

events.title: FedEx Shipment Pickup
events.description: A shipment was picked up by FedEx for NYSG LLC.

keyFacts: The total charges for the shipment amount to USD $5.50.
The shipment was picked up on August 1, 2003.
The billing and shipping address is the same: NYSG LLC, 457 Madison Ave, New York, NY 10022-6843.
